OL,3,CNew law for food allergen labels
OL,4,Cdelayed in Jersey
OL,6,FJersey's Environment Minister says the
OL,7,Fintroduction of a new law on labelling
OL,8,Ffood products with allergens has been
OL,9,Fdelayed.
OL,11,FResponding to Deputy Catherine
OL,12,FCurtis's written question to the
OL,13,FStates, Deputy Steve Luce said the
OL,14,F'departure of specialist staff' has
OL,15,Fdelayed the introduction of
OL,16,Fregulations which would see the
OL,17,Flabelling of allergens on food
OL,18,Fpackaging in the island.
