OL,3,CNew law for food allergen labels
OL,4,Cdelayed in Jersey
OL,6,FBringing in the Food Law (Jersey) 2023
OL,7,Fwould see Jersey bring its food
OL,8,Fallergen labelling legislation brought
OL,9,Fmore in line with UK and EU regulation.
OL,11,FDeputy Luce said that most food in
OL,12,FJersey is imported from the UK or EU
OL,13,Fwhere labelling allergens on food
OL,14,Fpackaging is already compulsory which
OL,15,Fhe believes gives people in the island
OL,16,F'an elevated level of consumer
OL,17,Fprotection'.
