OL,3,CNew law for food allergen labels
OL,4,Cdelayed in Jersey
OL,6,FIn 2023, Jersey's leading allergy
OL,7,Fexpert, Dr Matt Doyle, told ITV News
OL,8,Fthat Jersey was "behind" the UK and EU
OL,9,Fin passing laws on the labelling of
OL,10,Fallergens in food products.
OL,12,FThe UK Government passed a law in 2014
OL,13,Fto ensure allergen information is
OL,14,Fhighlighted on all pre-packaged food
OL,15,Fproducts.
OL,17,FThe EU passed a similar law in 2014 as
OL,18,Fwell.
